CodeClear.​NaturalDocs.​Engine.​Output.​Components.​JSSearchData
public
CodeClear.​NaturalDocs.​Engine.​Output.​Components.​JSSearchData

A helper class to build JavaScript search data for Output.Builders.HTML.  See <JavaScript Search Data> for the output format.

Usage

  • Create a JSSearchData object.

  • Call BuildPrefixIndex().

  • Call BuildPrefixDataFile().

Threading: Not Thread Safe

This class is only designed to be used by one thread at a time.  Each thread should create its own object.
